# Key mappings
unmap t
unmap x
unmap r
unmap b
unmap B
unmap o
unmap O
unmap T
unmap W

unmap d
map <c-d> scrollPageDown

unmap u
map <c-u> scrollPageUp

unmap J
map J nextTab

unmap K
map K previousTab

map < goBack
map > goForward

unmap H
unmap L
map H moveTabLeft
map L moveTabRight

map gb visitPreviousTab
map <c-6> visitPreviousTab
map <c-p> Vomnibar.activate
map <c-b> Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map <c-W> closeOtherTabs
map g0 lastTab

# Search engines
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
m: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google Maps
d: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s Duck
f: https://www.facebook.com/search/top?q=%s Facebook
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
